  "text": "[TO BE PUBLISHED IN THE GAZETTE OF INDIA, EXTRAORDINARY, PART II, SECTION 3, SUB-SECTION (i)] Government of India Ministry of Finance Department of Revenue Central Board of Excise and Customs Notification No. 3/2017 – Integrated Tax New Delhi, the 28 th June, 2017 7 Ashadha, 1939 Saka G.S.R. …..(E).— In exercise of the powers conferred by sub-section (3) of section 1 of the Integrated Goods and Services Tax Act, 2017 (13 of 2017), the Central Government hereby appoints the 1 st day of July, 2017, as the date on which the provisions of sections 4 to 13, 16 to 19, 21, 23 to 25 of the said Act, shall come into force. [F. No. 349/72/2017-GST] (Dr. Sreeparvathy S.L.) Under Secretary to the Government of India -- 1 of 1 --",
